title: Massive Wikileaks drop
author: VD
content_html:
I expect there is going to be a significant amount of news being generated by the latest Wikileaks data drop.

Wow!!! Wikileaks just dumped all of their files online. Everything from Hillary Clinton’s emails, McCains being guilty, Vegas shooting done by an FBI sniper, Steve Jobs HIV letter, PedoPodesta, Afghanistan, Syria, Iran, Bilderberg, CIA agents arrested for rape, WHO pandemic.

Happy Digging!

I haven’t seen anything damning yet, but it’s just a matter of time now, and not very much of it at that.
